>From Dr. Linthe, GFZ, I have received your request for when Brorfelde 
replaced Rude Sov in the Kp derivation, and the answer is:

Rude Skov was used until 15 March 1984, and consequently Brorfelde 
has been used from 16 March 1984 an onwards.

